253
00:15:02,918 --> 00:15:05,418
Okay, you got me.

254
00:15:05,488 --> 00:15:08,685
Look, you helped me feel better,

255
00:15:08,758 --> 00:15:10,592
and now I'll help you.

256
00:15:10,593 --> 00:15:12,394
You want to help me, Alan?

257
00:15:12,395 --> 00:15:15,695
Find a gun and shoot me in the eye.

258
00:15:15,831 --> 00:15:19,868
No, I was thinking I could give you
a chiropractic adjustment.

259
00:15:19,869 --> 00:15:23,605
You could also do my hair,
but what would be the point?

260
00:15:23,606 --> 00:15:26,775
Chiropractics
is not just about back ailments.

261
00:15:26,776 --> 00:15:29,911
It's a holistic approach
to wellness that includes

262
00:15:29,912 --> 00:15:32,447
unblocking pathways
in the nervous system

263
00:15:32,448 --> 00:15:35,488
so that the body can heal itself.

264
00:15:39,088 --> 00:15:41,886
Excuse me? What is...

265
00:15:43,125 --> 00:15:46,325
Alan. I never told you this before,

266
00:15:46,896 --> 00:15:50,776
but I guess now is as good a time as any.

267
00:15:51,467 --> 00:15:56,197
