at the Guadalajara Medical School.

294
00:17:16,719 --> 00:17:20,688
Since you're being honest,
I guess I can admit,

295
00:17:20,689 --> 00:17:24,049
I didn't really get into Guadalajara.

296
00:17:25,227 --> 00:17:29,697
I guess neither of us is doing exactly what
we dreamed about when we were kids.

297
00:17:29,698 --> 00:17:31,232
I guess not.

298
00:17:31,233 --> 00:17:33,668
But you know,
we could be doing a lot worse.

299
00:17:33,669 --> 00:17:36,169
Yes, we could.

300
